0.5.name: wordpress/bootstrap-admin
0.5.description:
A clean, minimalistic administration theme implementing Twitter's Bootstrap. Project was built by shoestrap.org and uses our very own Elusive-Icons webfont.

You can contribute by helping out in github: https://github.com/aristath/bootstrap-admin

This plugin will completely re-style your WordPress admin area, offering a cleaner experience. Coming soon: Complete rebranding for your WordPress Administration!

If you like this plugin and use it on your projects, please consider donating @ http://aristeides.com
